data.description: As soon as you drive up you will fall in love with this wonderful 2-bedroom/2-bathroom cottage style home with land in Burnet, TX. Charming with plenty of room to welcome family and friends inside & out. Once in the front door you will immediately notice the impeccable condition of this extremely well cared for home. Open living room concept that leads to a cozy dining room with a pathway to the kitchen. The kitchen has appliances with freshly painted cabinetry & ceramic plank tile floor. The perfect size master suite with a closet and a master bath with updated double vanities. The secondary bedroom is excellent size with closet. The patio/deck area overlooks a perfectly groomed spacious backyard with storage buildings for your convenience. Come morning or evening you will be nurtured with majestic, beautiful scenic views of the hill country. Property has convenient access to shopping/restaurants, entertainment and great schools. Call today for your showing request!
